      "content": "Hey, I'm looking for some help with a routing issue. I have a driver who has to hit 12 different drop-off points in one single loop and we need to minimize fuel and total mileage. Can you explain the best way to approach this kind of problem? Like, what's the logic for finding the most efficient path?",
